 Company intends to fund these payments", "bbox": [175.0, 692.9, 1061.4, 711.6]}, {"text": "from existing cash.", "bbox": [175.0, 720.0, 326.8, 738.7]}, {"text": "RECONCILIATION OF META PURCHASE ACCOUNTING LIABILITIES", "bbox": [175.0, 767.0, 797.9, 787.8]}, {"text": "In connection with the META acquisition, the Company recorded certain liabilities in purchase accounting under", "bbox": [175.0, 795.7, 1069.6, 814.5]}, {"text": "Emerging Issues Task Force Issue 95-3, “Recognition of Liabilities in Connection with a Purchase Combination”", "bbox": [175.0, 822.8, 1070.3, 841.5]}, {"text": "(“EITF 95-3”), for involuntary terminations, lease and contract terminations, and other costs. The Company expects", "bbox": [175.0, 849.9, 1096.9, 868.6]}, {"text": "the remaining exit costs to be paid in 2007, while the lease obligations will be paid over their respective contract", "bbox": [175.0, 877.0, 1071.9, 895.7]}, {"text": "periods through 2012. The Company is uncertain at this time regarding the timing of the settlement of the", "bbox": [175.0, 904.0, 1021.4, 922.8]}, {"text": "remaining tax contingencies. The Company intends to fund these payments from existing cash.", "bbox": [175.0, 931.1, 940.3, 949.9]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes the activity during 2006 and the ending balance at December 31, 2006 (in", "bbox": [175.0, 981.8, 1025.4, 1000.6]}, {"text": "thousands) under EITF 95-3:", "bbox": [175.0, 1008.9, 405.7, 1027.7]}, {"text": "Balance", "bbox": [436.9, 1055.1, 494.6, 1071.7]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [392.3, 1075.9, 494.7, 1092.6]}, {"text": "2005", "bbox": [457.6, 1096.7, 494.7, 1113.4]}, {"text": "Additional", "bbox": [532.6, 1075.9, 603.3, 1092.6]}, {"text": "Accruals (1)", "bbox": [519.7, 1096.7, 603.3, 1113.4]}, {"text": "Adjustments (2)", "bbox": [628.4, 1096.7, 739.8, 1113.4]}, {"text": "Payments (3)", "bbox": [764.9, 1096.7, 858.0, 1113.4]}, {"text": "Currency", "bbox": [907.5, 1055.1, 972.6, 1071.7]}, {"text": "Translation", "bbox